-- Croat Construction Firms to Build Arena in Qatar, Poslovni Says
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2012-12-05T07:15:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-05/croat-construction-firms-to-build-arena-in-qatar-poslovni-says.html
Croatian construction companies will
build an indoor sports stadium in Qatar,
 Constructionweekonline.com  reported, without saying how it got
the information.  The $130 million project, that will host the World Handball
Championship in Qatar in 2015, was secured after a visit to
Qatar last month by a  Croatian government  delegation, according
to the portal based in Dubai,  United Arab Emirates .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
 jkuzmanovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  